# A large fresh water [[lake]], on the border between [[Estonia]] and [[Russia]] in Northern Europe. It is the fifth largest lake in [[Europe]], and largest in Estonia. The lake consists of 3 parts: [[Lake Peipsi]] ([[Lake Chudskoe]]), [[Lake Pihkva]] ([[Lake Pskovskoe]]), [[Lake Lämmijärv]] ([[Lake Teploe]]).

